data.description: Completely Remodeled Spanish Style Single Family Home in a small Quiet Neighborhood...Brick paver courtyard in the front for entertaining friends and family, walking in front door you havea working fire place surrounding by new tile and freshly painted interior...large open kitchen with granite counters and new stainless steel appliances removes any worries...New hot water heater in the enclosed laundry room for ease of use...3 large bedrooms and 2 large finished bathrooms with new tile and vanities and space...lots of closet space and room for entertaining...Home also has Central AC to keep cool on those warm summer nights...Everything is NEW...simply pack your bags and move in.
